title: SID music: Flotsam - NULL Response (SIDFX 8580 dual mono bx_🎧)
description:
"NULL Response" (2022) by Flotsam/Pretzel Logic (Riku Ö). Art by Mikael/Pretzel Logic (Christopherjam palette used for more saturated colors).

Made using real C64 audio in SIDFX dual mono config (identical audio data for both chips):

Left channel: CSG 6582A 2792 25/Philippines NM235N18 1200T
Right channel: CSG 8580R5 0590 25/Hong Kong HH032232 HC-30

Project SIDFX:
http://www.sidfx.dk/
